{"tid":538510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母浸大學生會","createTime":"2018-01-23T16:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T11:46:58.000Z","uid":33959,"like":93,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"95720d891a0353c96d972dc628fbcedf128a6688","tid":538510,"uid":33959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T16:23:20.000Z","msg":"如果你係想入黎屌埋一份既sorry你可以出番去，但係希望大家可以睇埋先再決定屌唔屌<br />\n<br />\n冇錯學生會個P個「撚」字的確係好失策，但係以往幾年BU學生已經用過哂體制內、外嘅所有方法去表達訴求，但係校方嘅態度&hellip;大家都知，如果因為呢粒字就抹殺所有努力真係好唔公平。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係想話咩要反抗個制度你就先要跨過佢既，我想講，我pass左個豁免試，親身體驗過。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/002239_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F002239_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=73b1f814&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我只係一個普通嘅BU學生、學生會嘅基本會員，亦唔係任何soc嘅莊員，我知道我嘅身份實在係人微言輕，我明白BU只係一間普通大學，唔係d咩知名學府，亦唔會話咩浸大是我家、齊來愛護它，但係身為一個BU學生，我都好希望可以出一分力，令BU學生嘅身份唔再受人侮辱、誤解。<br />\n<br />\n最後附上懶人包，利伸：懶人包唔係我打<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@kenlui/%E6%A0%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C-%E8%AB%8B%E5%85%88%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8-%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98-%E8%AA%9E%E6%96%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%A0%E7%94%B1-34e5370766ed\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40kenlui%2F%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A1%258C-%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%2585%2588%25E4%25BA%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%25A0%2598-%25E8%25AA%259E%25E6%2596%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%2594%25B1-34e5370766ed&d=twUbOMYiiCgRTB8zOJLOKBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=62d29296\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@kenlui/%E6%A0%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C-%E8%AB%8B%E5%85%88%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%90%8C%E5%AD%B8-%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98-%E8%AA%9E%E6%96%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%A0%E7%94%B1-34e5370766ed</a>"},{"pid":"7d6fbe3f3a806598a1d289f6ccc60aeb83e3